commit.message: Fixed broken level that completed instantly.

Fix bug caused by newline characters in the level data.
Also fixed the level builder to not output these newline characters.
Added a new version of level 2 and autoformatted the levels.json file.
Move level data into JSON file and load that file dynamically.
Removed a space from a level because it is not obvious that it is there.
Focus on modal button so the keyboard can be used.
Covert levels.js to use prototype inheritance.
Move to EOF when down is pressed on the last line.
Fixed and added test for moving to a shorter line.
Fixed kill line functionality to delete/merge when at the end of a line.
Updated level 1 to make it more of a tutorial.

Fix level flow to allow full play-through.
Also allow dynamic modal generation.

Upgrade menu select screen. Added descriptive text about what the
user should do.
Also fixed layout flicker caused by collapsed dd elementss.
